These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: gardening, drawing
Job: musician, social-worker
1. Job:musician is in an even position##4
2. Job:social-worker == Hobby:drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | drawing | gardening |
| Job     | social-worker    | musician   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: tea, sprite
Sport: skateboarding, climbing
1. Sport:skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:sprite is on the left of Beverage:tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | sprite | tea        |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | climbing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: gospel, rock
Nationality: russian, indonesian
1. Nationality:russian is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:rock is on the left of Music-Genre:gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | gospel |
| Nationality   | russian | indonesian |

